name: WSJHeadlines
0:
”Alexa, open wall street journal headlines.”
”Alexa, launch wall street journal headlines.”
”Alexa, ask wall street journal headlines to send me the reading list.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wall street journal headlines
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Get today's top headlines from the WSJ Headlines on Alexa, any time, anywhere. Trusted, award-winning news at your fingertips
 With WSJ Headlines on Alexa, you can:
 - Get The WSJ Headlines most recent top five headlines.
 - Hear brief summaries of each article, so you can decide which news you want to learn more about.
 - Add articles to your reading list, and Alexa will email you links to read them later on web.
 You’ll never miss another piece of breaking news. Just say, “Alexa, open wall street journal headlines.” Or try, “Alexa, ask wall street journal headlines to send me the reading list.”
 Get the latest headlines from a world-renowned news source you can depend on. With The WSJ Headlines on Alexa, you’re always in the know.
